{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Legal_Matter",
  "title": "A Legal Matter",
  "summary": "At the Imperial Embassy on Caspar, the Vaathkree legal attache Nicholas Chang arrives seeking an audience with the spymaster Director Joir. After clearing reception, he is escorted into the conference chamber, where the Chief Diplomatic Officer Chantinelle Thistleborn -- caught lounging unprofessionally -- scrambles to attention. Chang, representing the Corporate Sector Authority, explains that the CSA's records of Imperial law are out of date and requests current legal documentation to avoid friction between the two powers, offering CSA documents in exchange on a datadisk. Joir, coolly noting the strategic value of the CSA alliance against the rising New Republic, agrees to provide copies of Imperial law through his diplomatic staff and directs further questions to Thistleborn. The brief, cordial meeting concludes with both sides exchanging contact information and parting on terms of careful mutual understanding.",
